title: Wholesale Price of Spun Silk Yarn, Domestic Gray for United States
notes:
Series Has Been Subdivided Into Three Variables: (1)-- Original Data, 1913-1932; (2)-- Original Data, 1932-1937; (3)-- Original Data, 1937-1939. Data Are The Averages Of One-Day-A-Week Quotations, Mill To Connecter, Quotations From The Manufacturer. Source: 1937 Data Are Direct From Bls; 1938-1939 Data From Bls Bulletins And "Wholesale Prices."

This NBER data series m04151c appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
